values: 街；街道；马路；（金融市场的非正式说法）华尔街；街式赛

word_mean_info__list.difference: 通常指市区外可以通行各种机动车辆的交通干线。
指从此处通往彼处的路线、路程等。
在美国，指城市中一侧或两侧建筑物林立的大道或马路；而在英国则常指通住乡村大住宅、私人大庄园或两旁栽树的道路。
指人或兽在森林、荒野或山中踩出的小径或崎岖小道。
尤指城市中的道路，往往一侧或两侧有高大建筑物；还可指城市小镇、近郊可供人、车、马行走的平坦道路。
多指由人或动物在田间、小丘或树丛中经常走动而踩出的小路，也指公园或花园等供人走的小径。
高速公路，新词，特指为车辆快速通行而修的专线，美语为freeway或expressway。
普通用词，含义广泛，可指各种路、道或通道，也可指抽象的道路。
指连接两地间供行人或车辆使用的广阔平坦的大道，多指公路，也可用于引申意义。
在英国，多指街道两旁的人行道，而美国人常用sidewlk表示人行道。
指农村或城镇的小道或小径，也指小巷。

bilingual.source: Her house is on the right of the street.
bilingual.target: 她的房子在街道的右边。

bilingual.source: The name of my street is Hatton Gardens.
bilingual.target: 我的街道名叫哈顿花园。
今天早上，街道成了一条河。

bilingual.source: Our street became a river very quickly.
bilingual.target: 我们的街道很快变成了一条河。

bilingual.source: Our street turned into a river in seconds.
bilingual.target: 我们的街道在几秒钟内变成了一条河。

bilingual.source: The street was icy — the car couldn't stop in time.
bilingual.target: 街道结冰了——车没能及时停下。

bilingual.source: The street it is on is filled with other businesses as well.
bilingual.target: 它所在的街道上还有其他企业。

list.abstract: street，英文单词，可用作名词、形容词，翻译为大街、街道等。
《STREET》是韩国女子组合EXID在2016年6月1日演唱的歌曲，全碟共13首歌曲。

yingyinNormal.en: You know actually, it does have a very interesting history. This street is the first street in the city to have an underground sewer system.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上这个地区的历史非常有趣，这条街是纽约第一条有下水道系统的街道。

yingyinNormal.en: I said I lived in a huge brownstone. On a nice street. With my two awesome parents. And my awesome dog named Daisy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我住在一个大的褐色砂石房子里。房子坐落在一个环境优雅的街道上。和我最爱的父母住在一起。还有一只叫黛西的狗。

yingyinNormal.en: This is a street in a city in a country called America, and Earth, that's a blue and green planet, always spinning, so I don't know why we don't fall off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一个城市里的一条街道，这个城市在一个叫美国的国家，国家在地球上，这是个蓝绿色的星球，一直在转，我不知道为什么我们不会掉下去。

yingyinNormal.en: I'II just pee in the street.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我到街上尿就好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Number one rule of Wall Street.
yingyinNormal.zh: 华尔街的第一定律。

yingyinNormal.en: What? I can't know street value?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么？！我就不能知道街头黑市价吗？！

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, well, I have street smarts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 行，聪明人脑子快，可我有街头智慧。

yingyinNormal.en: That is the word on the street, dear.
yingyinNormal.zh: 道上的确都是这么传的。

yingyinNormal.en: How about to the street say from the balcony?
yingyinNormal.zh: 何不从阳台把它丢到街上？

yingyinNormal.en: I, therefore, will match bail to street value.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我裁定保释金与毒品市值相等。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I'm gonna go back to being Street Phoebe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要当回街霸菲比。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you crazy? This is a street fight. The street has no rules.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是疯了不成？这是个街战街战，哪有什么规则的。

yingyinNormal.en: Some produce is so popular, it has its own street. Guess where we are? Pumpkin street. This is onion Street. And this is Marrow Street. Unsurprisingly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有些食品深受欢迎，成行成市了。猜猜我们在哪里？南瓜街。这是洋葱街。这个是西葫芦一条街。毫不奇怪。

yingyinNormal.en: No, it's none of those, we've accounted for those. St Margaret Street, Bridge Street, Sumatra Road, Parliament Street.
yingyinNormal.zh: 都不是，查过了，圣玛格丽特路，塔桥街，苏门答腊路，议会街。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm on the street, I'm going to cook you one of my favorite street-food dishes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在大街上，我将为你们烹调一道我最喜欢的街头小吃。

yingyinNormal.en: The hardware store's right down the street. There is a hardware store right down the street?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那间店就在街尾。街尾就有一间五金店吗？

yingyinNormal.en: It will for the people on the street. Oh, my God.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是街上的行人会看到绝美的风景了。天呐。

yingyinNormal.en: Word on the street, well, when I say street, I mean those little pretend streets they have here at the zoo. Of course.
yingyinNormal.zh: 道上的传闻，当我说“道上”的时候，我指的是园里的游园道路。当然了。

yingyinNormal.en: From opulent malls to the bustling markets of Temple Street and Ladies Street, tax-free Hong Kong is heaven bargain hunters.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从奢华的太古广场到大众化的庙街和女人街，都是购物的热点，而且香港的免税措施是精打细算人士的天堂。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't think I can. I don't have Howard's street cred.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能这么说。我没有霍华德那种街头痞子风。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: In a statement, the high <highlight>street</highlight> retailer defended itself by saying that the burnt clothing had failed safety tests.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一份声明中，高街零售商为自己辩护说，烧毁的衣服没有通过安全测试。

examination_example.sentence: A number of <highlight>street</highlight> artists around the world have started expressing themselves through a practice known as reverse graffiti (涂鸦) .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 世界各地的一些街头艺术家已经开始通过一种被称为“反向涂鸦”的做法来表达自己的想法。

examination_example.sentence: An office tower on Miller <highlight>Street</highlight> in Manchester is completely covered in solar panels.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 曼彻斯特米勒街的一座办公大楼完全被太阳能电池板覆盖。

examination_example.sentence: Up to 90, 000 tourists crowd its <highlight>streets</highlight> and canals every day — far outnumbering the 55, 000 permanent residents.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每天有多达90,000名游客拥挤在其街道和运河上，远远超过了这里的常住居民(55,000人)。

direction_info.description:

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: While riding his bike home on a cold night, he came across a sad-looking elderly woman wandering the <highlight>streets</highlight> by herself.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一个寒冷的夜晚，他骑着自行车回家时，遇到了一位面容悲伤的老妇人独自在街上徘徊。

examination_example.sentence: Now he hopes that other cities will consider making their <highlight>streets</highlight> run smarter instead of just making them bigger.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在，他希望其他城市会考虑让他们的街道运行得更智能，而不仅仅是让它们变得更大。

examination_example.sentence: What would Peter and his family like to do on Beale <highlight>Street</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 彼得和他的家人想在比Beale街做什么？

examination_example.sentence: As the hearse (灵车) went slowly through the <highlight>streets</highlight>, people said together “Grandpa Yuan, rest in peace” over and over again.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 灵车慢慢地穿过街道，人们一遍又一遍地说“袁爷爷，安息吧”。

examination_example.sentence: But even with five people now searching the town's <highlight>streets</highlight>, they had no luck.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但即使有五个人在镇上的街道上搜索，他们也没有运气。

examination_example.sentence: She used to sleep on the sidewalk of the Fifth <highlight>Street</highlight> Post Office.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她以前睡在第五街邮局的人行道上。

word_usage.usage: 表示“在某条街上”时，美国人多用on the street，英国人多用in the street。
